                <p class="entry-text text-justify" style="direction: ltr">
                  Looking for an exciting internship opportunity that will
                  kickstart your career in the mining industry?
                  <br />
                  Look no further than the Startup Internship Program! With
                  experienced mentors and predefined projects, you'll gain
                  invaluable insight into the world of R&D for new technologies
                  within the copper industry. Throughout this internship, you'll
                  have the opportunity to work alongside multiple teams and
                  learn about the innovative technologies being developed by
                  Kaniboom's startup teams. And as a bonus, you'll also have
                  access to complimentary training bootcamps hosted by Kaniboom.
                  <br />
                  Some of the topics you'll explore during this internship
                  include forming teams, conducting R&D, and gaining hands-on
                  experience with cutting-edge technologies.
                  <br />
                  Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to jumpstart your
                  career in the mining industry
                  <br />
                  Apply for the Startup Internship Program today!
                </p>
              </div>
